flowchart TD
    TDP[The Data Professor]
    CON[Constitution — 17 Rules]
    
    TDP -->|highest authority| CON
    
    CON --> GOV[Governance: 4 rules]
    CON --> DOC[Documentation: 4 rules]
    CON --> SEC[Security: 3 rules]
    CON --> HR[Human Resources: 4 rules]
    CON --> ENG[Engineering: 3 rules]
    CON --> FIN[Financial: 2 rules]
    
    GOV --> OBL1[OBLIGATION: REQ before impl]
    DOC --> OBL2[OBLIGATION: README updated]
    SEC --> PRO1[PROHIBITION: No hardcoded secrets]
    HR --> ESC1[ESCALATION: Gaps block execution]
    ENG --> OBL3[OBLIGATION: Follow specs]
    FIN --> OBL4[OBLIGATION: Respect budgets]
    
    CON --> VIO[Violations Registry]
    CON --> EXC[Exceptions Registry]
    
    VIO -->|repeated| TDP
    EXC -->|approval required| TDP
    
    style TDP fill:#ffd700,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style CON fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style GOV fill:#bbf,stroke:#333
    style DOC fill:#bfb,stroke:#333
    style SEC fill:#fbb,stroke:#333
    style HR fill:#fbf,stroke:#333
    style ENG fill:#ff9,stroke:#333
    style FIN fill:#9f9,stroke:#333
    style VIO fill:#f99,stroke:#333
    style EXC fill:#ff9,stroke:#333
